COURT ORDERED DEFENDANT REMANDED TO THE JUDGE ON RETURN OF THE BENCH WARRANT.

Defendant Jose Luis Gonzales not in court.  Joshua Mathy for Jesica Ballenger appeared for the State of Wisconsin.
Case is called on the record at approximately 4:10 p.m.  Attorney Ledesma was present in Court earlier this afternoon.  
This case is reassigned to Judge Rothstein, Branch 25.  Case was incorrectly assigned.  Defendant failing to appear, Court ordered a Bench Warrant to be issued.  Court ordered any bail posted to be forfeited.  State's motion for Judgment of Bond Forfeiture 30 days after notification from the Clerk of Circuit Court's Office is granted by the Court.  Court makes finding that there is a possible victim identifed, therefore, Court stays order of forfeiture with recompense to be determined at close of case.
